msgid "Convex hull"
msgstr "Casco convexo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1541
msgid "Calculates the convex hull for each feature in an input layer."
msgstr "Calcula el casco convexo para cada entidad en la capa de entrada."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1543
msgid ""
"See the 'Minimum bounding geometry' algorithm for a convex hull calculation "
"which covers the whole layer or grouped subsets of features."
msgstr ""
"Consulte el algoritmo 'Geometría de límite mínimo' para obtener un cálculo "
"de casco convexo que cubra toda la capa o subconjuntos agrupados de "
"entidades."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1550
msgid "Black lines identify the convex hull for each layer feature"
msgstr ""
"Las líneas negras identifican el casco convexo para cada entidad de capa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1558
msgid ":ref:`qgisminimumboundinggeometry`, :ref:`qgisconcavehull`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisminimumboundinggeometry`, \n"
":ref:`qgisconcavehull`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1577
