msgid "**Azimuth (degrees from North)**"
msgstr "**Azimuth (grados al Norte)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1652
msgid "``AZIMUTH``"
msgstr "``AZIMUTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1656
msgid "Angle (in degrees) as the middle value of the wedge"
msgstr "Ángulo (en grados) como el valor medio de la cuña"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1657
msgid "**Wedge width (in degrees)**"
msgstr "**Ancho de cuña (en grados)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1658
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5346
msgid "``WIDTH``"
msgstr "``WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1661
msgid "Default: 45.0"
msgstr "Preestablecido: 45.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1662
msgid ""
"Width (in degrees) of the buffer. The wedge will extend to half of the "
"angular width either side of the azimuth direction."
msgstr ""
"Ancho (en grados) del búfer. La cuña se extenderá hasta la mitad del ancho "
"angular a ambos lados de la dirección azimutal."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1669
msgid "Azimuth and width values of the wedge buffer"
msgstr "Azimut y valores de ancho del buffer de cuñas"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1671
msgid "**Outer radius**"
msgstr "**Radio exterior**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1672
msgid "``OUTER_RADIUS``"
msgstr "``OUTER_RADIUS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1676
msgid ""
"The outer *size* (length) of the wedge: the size is meant from the source "
"point to the edge of the wedge shape."
msgstr ""
"El *tamaño* exterior (longitud) de la cuña: el tamaño se entiende desde el "
"punto de origen hasta el borde de la forma de la cuña."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1679
msgid "**Inner radius**"
msgstr "**Radio Interior**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1681
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1758
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1856
