#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3228
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4044
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5359
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5549
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5563
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5713
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7579
msgid "Optional"
msgstr "Opcional"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1682
msgid "``INNER_RADIUS``"
msgstr "``INNER_RADIUS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1686
msgid "Inner radius value. If 0 the wedge will begin from the source point."
msgstr ""
"Valor de radio interior. Si es 0 la cuña empezará desde el punto origen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1688
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1711
msgid "**Buffers**"
msgstr "**Buffers**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1714
msgid "The output (wedge buffer) vector layer"
msgstr "La capa vectorial de salida (buffer de cuña)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1719
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:wedgebuffers``"
msgstr "**Algoritmo ID**: ``native:wedgebuffers``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1729
msgid "Delaunay triangulation"
msgstr "Triangulación Delaunay"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1730
msgid ""
"Creates a polygon layer with the Delaunay triangulation corresponding to the"
" input point layer."
msgstr ""
"Crea una capa poligonal mediante triangulación Delaunay correspondiendo a la"
" capa entrante de puntos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1736
msgid "Delaunay triangulation on points"
msgstr "Triangulación Delaunay en puntos"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1756
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4957
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5455
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6315
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6643
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7577
msgid "**Tolerance**"
msgstr "**Tolerancia**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1761
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4958
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5456
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6316
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6644
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7582
msgid "``TOLERANCE``"
msgstr "``TOLERANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1765
msgid ""
"Specifies an optional snapping tolerance which can be used to improve the "
"robustness of the triangulation."
msgstr ""
"Especifica una tolerancia de ajuste opcional que puede utilizarse para "
"mejorar la solidez de la triangulación."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1766
msgid "**Add point IDs to output**"
msgstr "**Añadir ID de puntos a la salida**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1769
msgid "``ADD_ATTRIBUTES``"
msgstr "``ADD_ATTRIBUTES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1773
msgid ""
"Specifies whether fields storing involved point features ID should be added "
"to the output. If False, an ``id`` field is used to identify the polygons."
msgstr ""
"Especifica si los campos que almacenan el ID de los objetos espaciales de "
"los puntos implicados deben añadirse a la salida. Si es falso, se utiliza un"
" campo ``id`` para identificar los polígonos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1775
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1799
msgid "**Delaunay triangulation**"
msgstr "**Triangulación Delaunay**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1802
msgid "The output (Delaunay triangulation) vector layer"
msgstr "La capa vectorial saliente (triangulación Delaunay)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1807
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:delaunaytriangulation``"
msgstr "**ID algoritmo**: ``native:delaunaytriangulation``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1817
msgid "Delete holes"
msgstr "Borrar agujeros"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1818
msgid ""
"Takes a polygon layer and removes holes in polygons. It creates a new vector"
" layer in which polygons with holes have been replaced by polygons with only"
" their external ring. Attributes are not modified."
msgstr ""
"Toma una capa de polígonos y elimina agujeros en polígonos. Crea una nueva "
"capa vectorial en la que los polígonos con agujeros han sido reemplazados "
"por polígonos con solo su anillo externo. Los atributos no se modifican."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1823
msgid ""
"An optional minimum area parameter allows removing only holes which are "
"smaller than a specified area threshold. Leaving this parameter at ``0.0`` "
"results in all holes being removed."
msgstr ""
"Un parámetro de área mínima opcional permite eliminar solo los agujeros que "
"son más pequeños que un umbral de área especificado. Si deja este parámetro "
"en `` 0.0 '', se eliminarán todos los agujeros."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1830
msgid "Before and after the cleaning"
msgstr "Antes y después de la limpieza"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1853
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2438
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3727
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5115
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7213
msgid "Input polygon vector layer"
msgstr "Capa vectorial de polígonos entrante"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1854
msgid "**Remove holes with area less than**"
msgstr "**Borra huecos con área menor que**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1857
msgid "``MIN_AREA``"
msgstr "``MIN_AREA``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1861
msgid ""
"Only holes with an area less than this threshold will be deleted. With a "
"value of ``0.0``, **all** the holes will be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Solo se eliminarán los agujeros con un área menor que este umbral. Con un "
"valor de ``0.0``, **todos** los agujeros serán eliminados."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1864
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1887
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5470
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5493
msgid "**Cleaned**"
msgstr "**Limpia**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1890
msgid "The output (cleaned) vector layer"
msgstr "La capa (limpia) vectorial saliente"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1895
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:deleteholes``"
msgstr "**Algoritmo ID**:  ``native:deleteholes``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1905
msgid "Densify by count"
msgstr "Densificar por conteo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1906
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1992
msgid ""
"Takes a polygon or line layer and generates a new one in which the "
"geometries have a larger number of vertices than the original one."
msgstr ""
"Toma una capa lieal o poligonal y genera una nueva en la cual las geometrías"
" tienen un número de vértices mayor que la original."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1909
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1999
msgid ""
"If the geometries have Z or M values present then these will be linearly "
"interpolated at the added vertices."
msgstr ""
"Si las geometrías tienen presentes valores Z o M estos serán interpolados "
"linealmente a los vértices añadidos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1912
msgid ""
"The number of new vertices to add to each segment is specified as an input "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"El número de nuevos vértices a añadir a cada segmento es especificado como "
"un parámetro de entrada."

