msgstr "0 --- Mayor Área"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2448
msgid "1 --- Smallest Area"
msgstr "1 --- Menor Área"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2449
msgid "2 --- Largest Common Boundary"
msgstr "2 --- Frontera común mas larga"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2451
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2474
msgid "**Eliminated**"
msgstr "**Eliminado**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2477
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3920
msgid "The output polygon vector layer."
msgstr "La capa vectorial poligonal saliente"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2482
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:eliminateselectedpolygons``"
msgstr "**Algoritmo ID**: ``qgis:eliminateselectedpolygons``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2492
msgid "Explode lines"
msgstr "Explotar lineas"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2493
msgid ""
"Takes a lines layer and creates a new one in which each line layer is "
"replaced by a set of lines representing the segments in the original line."
msgstr ""
"Toma una capa de líneas y crea una nueva en la que cada capa de línea se "
"reemplaza por un conjunto de líneas que representan los segmentos en la "
"línea original."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2497
msgid ""
"Each line in the resulting layer contains only a start and an end point, "
"with no intermediate vertices between them."
msgstr ""
"Cada línea en la capa resultante contiene solo un punto inicial y final, sin"
" vértices intermedios entre ellos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2500
msgid ""
"If the input layer consists of CircularStrings or CompoundCurves, the output"
" layer will be of the same type and contain only single curve segments."
msgstr ""
"Si la capa de entrada está formada por CircularStrings o CompoundCurves, la "
"capa de salida será del mismo tipo y solo contendrá segmentos de curva "
"únicos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2506
