msgstr "Filtrar vértices por valor de M"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3073
msgid ""
"Filters away vertices based on their M value, returning geometries with only"
" vertex points that have a M value greater than or equal to the specified "
"minimum value and/or less than or equal to the maximum value."
msgstr ""
"Filtra los vértices en función de su valor M, devolviendo geometrías con "
"solo puntos de vértice que tienen un valor M mayor o igual que el valor "
"mínimo especificado y / o menor o igual que el valor máximo."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3078
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3179
msgid ""
"If the minimum value is not specified then only the maximum value is tested,"
