#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3618
msgid ""
"Creates a point geometry interpolated at a set distance along line or curve "
"geometries."
msgstr ""
"Crea una geometría de punto interpolada a una distancia establecida a lo "
"largo de geometrías de línea o curva."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3621
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3782
msgid "Z and M values are linearly interpolated from existing values."
msgstr ""
"Los valores Z y M se interpolan linealmente de los valores existentes."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3623
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3784
msgid ""
"If a multipart geometry is encountered, only the first part is considered "
"when calculating the substring."
msgstr ""
"Si se encuentra una geometría multiparte, solo se considera la primera parte"
" al calcular la subcadena."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3626
msgid ""
"If the specified distance is greater than the input feature's length, the "
"resultant feature will have a null geometry."
msgstr ""
"Si la distancia especificada es mayor que la longitud de la entidad de "
"entrada, la entidad resultante tendrá una geometría nula."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3632
msgid "Interpolated point at 500m of the beginning of the line"
msgstr "Punto interpolado a 500 m del comienzo de la línea."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3634
msgid ":ref:`qgispointsalonglines`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgispointsalonglines`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3657
msgid "Distance from the beginning of the line"
msgstr "Distancia desde el comienzo de la línea"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3658
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3681
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4796
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4819
msgid "**Interpolated points**"
msgstr "**Puntos interpolados**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3684
msgid ""
"The output point vector layer with features at a set distance along the line"
" or polygon boundary"
msgstr ""
"La capa vectorial saliente de punto con entidades a una distancia "
"establecida a lo largo de la línea o el límite del polígono"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3690
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:interpolatepoint``"
msgstr "**Algoritmo ID**: ``native:interpolatepoint``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3700
msgid "Keep N biggest parts"
msgstr "Mantener N partes mayores"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3701
msgid ""
"Takes a layer with polygons or multipolygons and returns a new layer in "
"which only the *n* largest polygons of each multipolygon feature are kept. "
"If a feature has *n* or fewer parts, the feature will just be copied."
msgstr ""
"Toma una capa con polígonos o multipolígonos y devuelve una nueva capa en la"
" que solo se mantienen los polígonos más grandes * n * de cada entidad "
"multipolígono. Si una entidad tiene * n * o menos partes, la entidad solo se"
" copiará."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3709
msgid ""
"Clockwise from top left: original multipart feature, one, two and three "
"biggest parts kept"
msgstr ""
"En el sentido de las agujas del reloj desde la parte superior izquierda: "
"función multiparte original, una, dos y tres partes más grandes"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3724
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3894
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3917
msgid "**Polygons**"
msgstr "**Polígonos**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3728
msgid "**Parts to keep**"
msgstr "**Partes a mantener**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3729
msgid "``PARTS``"
msgstr "``PARTS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3730
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4231
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6549
